    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">  
</head>
<body>
  
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

<!-- Hero Section con imagen horizontal -->
<section class="hero-artrate">
  <img src="images assessment/Woman Delivering Speech at Podium.jpeg" alt="ARTRATE Banner">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>ARTRATE</h1>
    <p>Your voice shapes the future of art education</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Sección 2: Título principal ARTRATE -->
<section class="main-title">
  <h1><strong>ART-RATE</strong></h1>
</section>

<!-- Sección 3: Segunda galería de imágenes -->
<section class="image-gallery">
  <div class="gallery-row">
    <div class="image-box">
      <img src="images assessment/Creative Woman at Her Studio Desk.jpeg" alt="Artwork 4">
    </div>
    <div class="image-box">
      <img src="images assessment/Joyful Group Interaction.jpeg" alt="Artwork 5">
    </div>
    <div class="image-box">
      <img src="images assessment/Contemplative Woman with Humankind Sweatshirt.jpeg" alt="Artwork 6">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Sección 4: Subtítulo profesional -->
<section class="subtitle-section">
  <h2>Why Is Your Voice Valuable to Us?</h2>
</section>

<!-- Sección 5: Explicación del valor de la opinión -->
<section class="importance-text">
  <p>Your feedback helps us grow and improve.</p>
  <p>It also supports future students in making the decision to become part of the Solent Art family.</p>
</section>

<!-- Sección 6: Reseñas de estudiantes -->
 <!-- Sección 6: Reseñas de estudiantes -->
<section class="reviews-section">
  <div class="review-box">
    <img src="images assessment/Black and White Portrait of a Woman.jpeg" alt="Student 1">
    <div class="review-text">
      <h3>Maria Rossi</h3>
      <p>Graphic Design</p>
      <p>"Studying at Solent Art helped me find my creative voice.  
      The environment is welcoming and truly inspiring.  
      Tutors support your vision and personal growth.  
      I gained both artistic skills and confidence.  
      Collaborating with classmates was a joy.  
      I'm proud to call this place my second home."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="review-box">
    <img src="images assessment/Man in Green Uniform.jpeg" alt="Student 2">
    <div class="review-text">
      <h3>James Wilson</h3>
      <p>Photography</p>
      <p>"My time here has been nothing short of amazing.  
      The campus has excellent facilities for photographers.  
      I learned how to build a strong visual narrative.  
      Every teacher pushed me to explore my creativity.  
      The projects were both fun and challenging.  
      This journey shaped me into a real artist."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="review-box">
    <img src="images assessment/Contemplative Artist in Studio.jpeg" alt="Student 3">
    <div class="review-text">
      <h3>Elena García</h3>
      <p>Illustration</p>
      <p>"Solent Art gave me the tools to express my ideas.  
      The courses are flexible and creatively open.  
      I loved learning with passionate classmates.  
      Teachers here care deeply about your success.  
      I now feel prepared for my professional career.  
      This experience exceeded my expectations."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="review-box">
    <img src="images assessment/men(deco 2).jpeg" alt="Student 4">
    <div class="review-text">
      <h3>Lucas Martin</h3>
      <p>Fine Arts</p>
      <p>"At Solent Art, I discovered my artistic identity.  
      The freedom to explore styles is priceless.  
      We had access to amazing studios and mentors.  
      My confidence as a painter grew so much.  
      I felt constantly challenged and supported.  
      This school helped me reach my potential."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="review-box">
    <img src="images assessment/Woman Enjoying Music.jpeg" alt="Student 5">
    <div class="review-text">
      <h3>Sophia Ahmed</h3>
      <p>Fashion Design</p>
      <p>"I chose Solent Art for its vibrant fashion program.  
      The teachers helped turn ideas into reality.  
      We created collections with real-world impact.  
      I felt inspired by the creativity around me.  
      The university truly nurtures bold designers.  
      I’m excited for what comes next in fashion."</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="review-box">
    <img src="images assessment/Artisan at Work.jpeg" alt="Student 6">
    <div class="review-text">
      <h3>Tom Becker</h3>
      <p>Animation</p>
      <p>"Animation was always my dream, and now it’s real.  
      Solent Art gave me the skills to bring ideas to life.  
      I loved working on projects with other creatives.  
      We had access to the best software and studios.  
      Each class pushed my imagination further.  
      I'm now building a strong career in animation."</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</section>
<!-- Final Section: Imagen + Texto del evento -->
<section class="open-day-section">
  <div class="open-day-container">
    <div class="open-day-image">
      <img src="images assessment/Contemplative Audience Member with Headphones.jpeg" alt="Open Day Invitation">
    </div>
    <div class="open-day-text">
      <h2>Want to hear more stories?</h2>
      <p>Come to our Open Day to meet our students and professors. Discover their experiences and become part of our creative community.</p>
      
      <div class="event-box">
        <h3>Open Day Event</h3>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> Saturday, June 15, 2025</p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> 10:00 AM - 2:00 PM</p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> Solent Art University - Main Campus</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
